where the <HI>Swedish</HI> Ambassadors met them, <HI>in</HI>
order to their going together into <HI>Muscovy. p.</HI> 4</ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<HEAD>MAY.</HEAD>
<ITEM>The 15. leave <HI>Reuel</HI> and return to <HI>Narva</HI> the
