<P>Besides all these, there are yet some five or six and twenty, who have each of them ten
thousand <HI>Kockiens</HI> of yearly Revenue. But we shall forbear the naming of them.</P>
<P>It remains then only, that we give an account of the Revenues of those Lords who are
actually attendant on the Court, which are so considerable, that they may well deserve a
place by themselves.
<LIST>
